<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id7a47545d-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1990—<ref href="/us/pl/101/382">Pub. L. 101–382</ref> substituted “1991 and 1992” for “1989 and 1990”.</p>
